814
00:42:10,570 --> 00:42:11,600
Okay.

815
00:42:13,470 --> 00:42:15,300
What dough is that?

816
00:42:16,610 --> 00:42:18,040
We prepared...

817
00:42:18,170 --> 00:42:21,080
