818
00:42:22,750 --> 00:42:24,280
What's "baba?"

819
00:42:24,410 --> 00:42:26,979
Baba is a French dessert.

820
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:30,320
Koreans might find it unfamiliar.

821
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:33,390
- It's my 1st time hearing it. - It's my 1st time too.

822
00:42:33,420 --> 00:42:36,729
It's dipped in a syrup which uses rum, the liquor.

823
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:41,060
Then, cream or fruit is placed on top of it.

824
00:42:41,160 --> 00:42:44,269
When the bread is first served, it's a bit hard.

825
00:42:44,270 --> 00:42:45,829
But once it's drenched in sweet syrup,

826
00:42:45,830 --> 00:42:49,339
the syrup seeps in slowly, which reminds us of flirting.

827
00:42:49,340 --> 00:42:50,540
So we chose baba.

828
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:53,639
It's hard to find a Korean who likes it.

829
00:42:53,640 --> 00:42:55,139
- Really? Why? - Baba is?

830
00:42:55,140 --> 00:42:56,379
- In France, - Really?

831
00:42:56,380 --> 00:42:59,179
the alcohol is so strong that you could get drunk.

832
00:42:59,180 --> 00:43:01,619
Not everyone likes it because of the strong alcohol taste?

833
00:43:01,620 --> 00:43:02,649
That's one thing.

834
00:43:02,650 --> 00:43:05,319
Korean pastry and desserts don't use alcohol much.

835
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:06,860
- That's right. - But it's common in Europe.

836
00:43:06,890 --> 00:43:09,690
So it's not exactly a safe move.

837
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:15,829
Let's give them a sense of unity by using vanilla syrup.

838
00:43:15,830 --> 00:43:17,199
- All 3 of them? - For all 3.

839
00:43:17,200 --> 00:43:18,270
I got it.

840
00:43:18,430 --> 00:43:21,470
And a bit of...

841
00:43:23,970 --> 00:43:27,710
The tiniest bit of whiskey.

842
00:43:27,940 --> 00:43:30,050
Whiskey? No, we shouldn't.

843
00:43:30,650 --> 00:43:31,910
I'm totally against using liquor.

844
00:43:38,220 --> 00:43:39,759
How many percent of this syrup is liquor?

845
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:41,319
- Quite a lot. - Right?

846
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:44,930
About a third of the whole syrup is liquor.

847
00:43:48,930 --> 00:43:50,969
I personally think...

848
00:43:50,970 --> 00:43:54,540
Koreans aren't fond of desserts with liquor.

849
00:43:55,700 --> 00:43:57,440
Rum baba itself...

850
00:43:57,840 --> 00:43:59,680
