854
00:44:06,450 --> 00:44:09,750
was a dangerous move.

855
00:44:10,350 --> 00:44:11,649
Should we add alcohol?

856
00:44:11,650 --> 00:44:13,919
I'm strongly against adding it.

857
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:15,120
A bit of bourbon whiskey...

858
00:44:16,190 --> 00:44:18,660
- Shall I work on the lemons? - Sure, take them.

859
00:44:25,330 --> 00:44:29,340
So the syrup will be infused with the citrus fragrance...

860
00:44:31,910 --> 00:44:34,210
Gosh, this... Thank you.

861
00:44:36,850 --> 00:44:38,510
They're adding alcohol.

862
00:44:39,680 --> 00:44:42,050
- Shall we add it now? - Okay, let's.

863
00:44:42,280 --> 00:44:43,549
We'll pour them from each side, right?

864
00:44:43,550 --> 00:44:45,350
- Yes. - From each side.

865
00:44:46,220 --> 00:44:47,360
One, two, three.

866
00:44:52,530 --> 00:44:55,930
- They're adding rum. - Rum, vanilla, oranges, and lemons.

867
00:45:02,300 --> 00:45:04,370
We decided to just add...

868
00:45:04,840 --> 00:45:06,510
