871
00:45:12,480 --> 00:45:14,349
As long as we manage to get rid of the alcohol taste,

872
00:45:14,350 --> 00:45:17,190
adding liquor would be so much better.

873
00:45:17,390 --> 00:45:18,750
So I caved in.

874
00:45:21,860 --> 00:45:23,760
- She's setting it on fire. - It's ignited.

875
00:45:30,300 --> 00:45:32,570
How long does it take?

876
00:45:32,940 --> 00:45:34,339
Once all the alcohol evaporates,

877
00:45:34,340 --> 00:45:36,809
- the fire goes out on its own. - Really?

878
00:45:36,810 --> 00:45:39,340
What matters is how well they got rid of the alcohol taste...

879
00:45:39,810 --> 00:45:42,280
and how well they retained the zest.

880
00:45:43,780 --> 00:45:45,280
It's boiling hot.

881
00:45:47,920 --> 00:45:50,019
- Okay, nice. - Good.

882
00:45:50,020 --> 00:45:51,420
- Good. - It's pretty.

883
00:45:53,060 --> 00:45:56,290
You need to make baba dry when baking,

884
00:45:56,530 --> 00:45:59,259
then add moisture to it by adding syrup.

885
00:45:59,260 --> 00:46:01,700
So the dryness of it is important too.

886
00:46:03,770 --> 00:46:04,930
- Let's soak it. - Yes.

887
00:46:06,440 --> 00:46:07,440
Let's see.

888
00:46:13,680 --> 00:46:14,980
- It's just nice. - Okay.

889
00:46:24,250 --> 00:46:27,020
We prepared three desserts today.

890
00:46:27,720 --> 00:46:30,589
The more you eat, the more you'll flirt,

891
00:46:30,590 --> 00:46:33,860
